Method Detail

millisBeforeStartup

public static java.lang.Long millisBeforeStartup(java.lang.String cfgId)
Get the duration to wait after finishing the loading of the given package before the execution of auto-setup for adapter settings starts. The key to be checked is "wx.config.autoSetup.adapter.sleepMillis.startup". If this package does not contain the respective setting, the global value will be checked. For that the same key is read from the package . If this is also not defined or set to a value of <=0, the auto-setup execution starts immediately.

Parameters:
cfgId - Package for which to perform this check
Returns:
Number of milliseconds for specified package; setting
